    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The TELC B1 Mündlicher Ausdruck (Speaking) module takes approximately 15 minutes with a 20-minute preparation phase (Vorbereitungszeit). The exam can be conducted as a pair or individual examination (Paar- oder Einzelprüfung)."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Einander kennenlernen (Getting to Know Each Other)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Introduce yourself: name, residence, family, profession, hobbies"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Decide 'du' or 'Sie' based on the situation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Gespräch über ein Thema (Discussion on a Topic)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Each partner receives a short text with a different opinion on the same topic"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Summarize your text, listen to your partner, then discuss"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Gemeinsam etwas planen (Planning Together)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• Plan something together (party, trip, event)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Make suggestions and react to partner's ideas"
    },
    {
